modules.description: Provides functions for parsing and rendering CommonMark documents, with support for an unsafe flag to bypass certain safety checks. Operates on document nodes, allowing traversal and manipulation of structured markup data. Used to enhance a static site generator by enabling direct access to and modification of parsed document content.

Converts CommonMark text to HTML, XML, man pages, LaTeX, and back to CommonMark format using specified rendering flags. Processes input as strings or files, parsing into an internal representation and rendering with customizable options. Supports detailed control over formatting and output width for structured text transformation.
